 Restaurant Data Analysis â€“ Power BI Dashboard
An interactive multi-page Power BI dashboard providing insights into restaurant trends, cuisines, price ranges, ratings, delivery modes, and city-level performance.
 Project Overview

This Power BI report analyzes restaurant data collected from multiple cities.
It offers a detailed understanding of:

Popular cuisines

City-wise restaurant distribution

Customer preferences (online delivery, table booking)

Price ranges and affordability

Ratings and reviews

Geographic insights using maps

Comparison of independent restaurants vs chains

The dashboard contains multiple connected pages, providing a complete end-to-end view of the restaurant landscape.
