 How to View the Dashboard
ğŸ”¹ Option 1 â€” Download the PBIX File

Click on Restaurant_Dashboard.pbix

Select Download raw file

Open in Power BI Desktop (MSI version recommended)

Use the navigation buttons to explore the pages

ğŸ”¹ Option 2 â€” View Screenshots

All dashboard pages are available under the /previews folder for quick reference.

 File Protection

The PBIX file is configured so that:

Users can view pages

Buttons & visuals remain interactive

They cannot overwrite the original design

They must save a new copy if they try to modify anything

This keeps the original dashboard secure.

Dataset Description

The dataset contains:

Restaurant ID & Name

City, Locality

Cuisine Types

Price Range, Cost for Two

Online Delivery & Table Booking Availability

Latitude, Longitude

Aggregate Rating, Rating Text & Color

Votes

The dataset used for this report is located in /data/Dataset.csv.
